      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study performed (coarse 4.2M, medium 8.7M, fine 17.1M cells). GCI on hemolysis index is 8.3%, exceeding the 5% threshold. Asymptotic range confirmed (GCI ratio 1.02). Achieved level 3 — GCI computed but threshold not met."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
