      "rationale": "FDA pump experiments used glycerol-water blood analog. Inlet velocity profiles measured by LDV with ±3% uncertainty. Fluid viscosity matched at 37 °C. However, hematocrit-dependent rheology not replicated in analog fluid, and pulsatile inlet waveform not applied in validation experiments. Significant gap at required level 5."
    },
