      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative validation metric (E_val) computed with uncertainty bounds; model bias within ±15% of experimental hemolysis index across all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "E_val computed at 5 operating points. Bias ranges from -8% to +31%. Three of five points within ±15%; two points exceed threshold at high-flow low-speed conditions. Uncertainty intervals overlap at 3 of 5 points. Achieved level 3 — partial agreement with documented outliers."
