      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) used as both validation and COU QoI. Direct correspondence confirmed. Minor gap: validation experiments used in-vitro cell-free hemoglobin assay whereas COU predicts in-vivo hemolysis — physiological differences acknowledged but not quantified. Achieved level 4."
    },
