      "rationale": "Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model selected without formal model form uncertainty analysis. Alternative hemolysis models (Goubergrits, Taskin) not evaluated. Model form uncertainty is the dominant epistemic uncertainty source at MRL 5 but has not been assessed."
