      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ initiated: 6 of 11 uncertain inputs have assigned distributions. Remaining 5 inputs (including blood viscosity temperature dependence and red blood cell fragility index) assigned uniform distributions as placeholders. Convergence of Monte Carlo not demonstrated (N=500 samples, no bootstrap CI on variance). Partially initiated but not assessed at required level 5."
