    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors assessed; six flagged as epistemic gaps. Despite multiple achieved levels below required levels, the assessment team determined that the Monte Carlo UQ framework provides sufficient uncertainty characterization for the intended submission context, and that the hemolysis index predictions are conservative relative to the clinical threshold. Decision: Accepted with documented gaps pending resolution prior to final regulatory submission.",
